<div>
  <div class="margin-bottom-5">&larr; <%= link_to 'path', root_path %></div>
  <h1>Add new organization</h1>
  <h2>Organization added!</h2>
  <div class="usa-alert usa-alert--success">
    <div class="usa-alert__body">
      <h4 class="usa-alert__heading">Success status</h4>
      <p class="usa-alert__text">This is a succinct, helpful success message.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p>To manage your organization's credentials, you can assign a Credential Delegate (CD). 
    This person will be responsible for submitting your organization's technical requirements 
    and managing your access to the DPC API.
  </p>
  <p>Learn more about the Credential Delegate role.</p>
  <div class="margin-top-5">
    <div class="display-flex flex-row flex-start" style="gap:20px;">
        <div class="flex-align-self-center">
            <%= render Core::Button::ButtonComponent.new(label: 'Assign CD now', destination: new_organization_credential_delegate_invitation_path(@organization))%>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-align-self-center">
            <%= link_to 'Assign CD later', root_path %>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
